    public class v0GantryAnimation
extends javax.swing.JPanel
implements java.awt.event.ActionListener
    CSCI200: Kitting Cell Project v0GantryAnimation is a panel class in which the components for the factory animation are instantiated and animated. Variables: ArrayList underParts, parts, overParts: Designate draw order such that parts don't overlap poorly Timer timer Agents and GUI Components: Gantry, Feeder, Diverter, Lane x2, Nest x2
    Author:
    Jessica Yoshimi

        public v0GantryAnimation()
